Console.WriteLine (myDirectoryEntry.Name + " entry is created in container.");  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a0ddf-113">O exemplo C++ a seguir cria um novo <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> com um caminho especificado do objeto, em seguida, cria uma nova entrada no contêiner e salva-o.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a0ddf-113">The following C++ example creates a new <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> object with a specified path, then creates a new entry in the container and saves it.</span></span>  
  
